"Everything's fine. I can take care of myself, and the others."
"Another hero who keeps claiming he's fine, even as he bleeds to death."
"You're not a sissy, I give you that. And you're right! Those scratches are nothing!"
"Aren't you the one who always says I should take better care of myself? Don't be so stubborn, Tristian, and let us check your wounds."
"You're going to fall over, if anyone so much as taps you on the shoulder. Though I guess that's true even on your good days, ha, ha!"
